definition.value: A 1-alkyl-2,3-diacylglycerol in which the acyl group at position 2 is specified as acetyl.
A steroid sulfate that is the 3-sulfate of estrone.
An amino dicarboxylic acid that is  malonic acid in which one of the methylene hydrogens has been replaced by an amino group.
A glycerophosphoethanolamine compound having an alk-1-enyl substituent at the 1-position and an acyl substituent at the 2-position.
